REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","en","Wood Anatomy of <I>Thuja sutchuenensis</I> Endemic to China","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract975.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","en","Plant Science Journal","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract975.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","en","The wood anatomy of <I>Thuja sutchuenensis</I>,an endangered plant endemic to China,is observed for the first time under optical and scanning electron microscopes.Growth rings are delineated by a narrow darker band of thick-walled latewood tracheids with abrupt transition from earlywood(EW)to latewood(LW).Longitudinal tracheids are relatively short with an average value of 1.61±0.22 mm in EW tracheids and 1.74±0.26 mm in LW tracheids.The bordered pits are mostly uniseriate,warty layer occasionally occurred on the pit margo.Cross fields are predominantly taxodioid with 2-6(8)pits.Xylem rays are mostly uniseriate with 1-11(2-5)cells in height and 65-70 rays per mm<SUP>2</SUP> in density,among which nodular and indenture structure is apparent.The observation shows that the main characters of <I>T.sutchuenensis</I> wood are similar to those in other four species of this genus,providing evidence for the further investigation of <I>T.sutchuenensis</I>.","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract975.shtml");
REPLACE INTO publications(authors,title,year,journal,spage,epage,volume,issue,pdf,url,date,abstract,issn,guid) values("刘仲健;陈心启;金效华","耳唇槽舌兰——中国兰科一新种","2005","植物科学学报",154,156,"23","2","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/article/downloadArticleFile.do?attachType=PDF&id=1032","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1032.shtml","2005-04-25","对产于云南的兰科新种耳唇槽舌兰(<I>Holcoglossum auriculatum</I>)进行了描述和绘图。该新种具有显著特征:萼片与花瓣基部有长爪;花瓣边缘具不规则齿或呈啮蚀状;唇瓣椭圆状圆形,边缘有短流苏或啮蚀状流苏,基部有爪和耳,极易区别于该属已知的种类,包括它的近缘种白唇槽舌兰(<I>H.subulifolium</I>)。","1000-470X","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1032.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","zh","刘仲健;陈心启;金效华","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1032.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","zh","耳唇槽舌兰——中国兰科一新种","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1032.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","zh","植物科学学报","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1032.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","zh","对产于云南的兰科新种耳唇槽舌兰(<I>Holcoglossum auriculatum</I>)进行了描述和绘图。该新种具有显著特征:萼片与花瓣基部有长爪;花瓣边缘具不规则齿或呈啮蚀状;唇瓣椭圆状圆形,边缘有短流苏或啮蚀状流苏,基部有爪和耳,极易区别于该属已知的种类,包括它的近缘种白唇槽舌兰(<I>H.subulifolium</I>)。","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1032.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","en","LIU Zhong-Jian;CHEN Sing-Chi;JIN Xiao-Hua","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1032.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","en","<I>Holcoglossum auriculatum</I>,A New Species ofOrchidaceae from China","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1032.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","en","Plant Science Journal","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1032.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","en","<I>Holcoglossum auriculatum</I> Z.J.Liu,S.C.Chen et X.H.Jin,a new species of Orchidaceae from Yunnan,is described and illustrated.This is a remarkable new species quite distinct from those known to us,including its ally <I>H.subulifolium</I>(Rchb.f.)Christenson,by having long-clawed sepals and petals,irregularly denticulate- or erose-margined petals and a peculiar lip which is elliptic-orbicular,shortly fimbriate or erose-fimbriate on the margins and clawed and auriculate at the base.","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1032.shtml");
REPLACE INTO publications(authors,title,year,journal,spage,epage,volume,issue,pdf,url,date,abstract,issn,guid) values("王孝安;段仁燕;王明利","太白红杉单木胸径生长模型的研究","2005","植物科学学报",157,162,"23","2","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/article/downloadArticleFile.do?attachType=PDF&id=1033","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1033.shtml","2005-04-25","通过比较分析4种有代表性的植物竞争指数的预测效果,选择较合适的指标构建太白红杉(<I>Larix chinensis</I>)的单木生长模型。研究结果表明:包含对象木胸径、竞争木胸径及对象木与竞争木距离的APA指数能客观反映太白红杉群落植株间的竞争关系;以近2年内胸径相对生长速率为因变量,自身胸径大小和竞争强度为自变量,通过回归分析建立的太白红杉单木生长模型具有较高的回归优度(<I>r</I>=0.916,<I>P</I>&lt;0.05),表明该模型能很好地预测太白红杉的生长。","1000-470X","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1033.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","zh","王孝安;段仁燕;王明利","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1033.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","zh","太白红杉单木胸径生长模型的研究","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1033.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","zh","植物科学学报","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1033.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","zh","通过比较分析4种有代表性的植物竞争指数的预测效果,选择较合适的指标构建太白红杉(<I>Larix chinensis</I>)的单木生长模型。研究结果表明:包含对象木胸径、竞争木胸径及对象木与竞争木距离的APA指数能客观反映太白红杉群落植株间的竞争关系;以近2年内胸径相对生长速率为因变量,自身胸径大小和竞争强度为自变量,通过回归分析建立的太白红杉单木生长模型具有较高的回归优度(<I>r</I>=0.916,<I>P</I>&lt;0.05),表明该模型能很好地预测太白红杉的生长。","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1033.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","en","WANG Xiao-An;DUAN Ren-Yan;WANG Ming-Li","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1033.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","en","Study on DBH Increment Model of Individual Trees Growing for <I>Larix chinensis</I>","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1033.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","en","Plant Science Journal","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1033.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","en","<I>Larix chinensis</I>,listed in Chinese <I>Plant Red Data Book</I>,is a typical endemic species in Qinling Mountain.It is the only tree species that structures the pure forest locates 2600-(3600 m),which has special functions to conserve water,firm mountain stone and maintain water and soil at the timberline area.We present a model for predicting the diameter at breast height(DBH)growth of <I>L.chinensis</I>.Data for this study were collected in Taibai Mountain Natural(Reserve),Shaanxi Province,China.Four samples of 40 m×40 m were investigated and every plant was stem-mapped.Species,DBH,total height,and crown length were recorded for each tree that had reached a diameter of 5 cm at breast height.Area potentially available index(APA),reflecting objectively the competition and growth pattern of <I>L.chinensis</I>,was selected in this paper.Taking subjective DBH and competition index as independent variables and the two yearly DBH relative growth rate as dependent variable,the growth model was established with good regression result.The <I>r</I>-value was 0.916 and the <I>P</I> value was less than 0.05.The model can simulate and predict the growth for <I>L.chinensis</I> efficiently.","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1033.shtml");
REPLACE INTO publications(authors,title,year,journal,spage,epage,volume,issue,pdf,url,date,abstract,issn,guid) values("周正立;李志军;龚卫江;高山","胡杨、灰叶胡杨开花生物学特性研究","2005","植物科学学报",163,168,"23","2","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/article/downloadArticleFile.do?attachType=PDF&id=1041","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1041.shtml","2005-04-25","从居群水平研究了胡杨、灰叶胡杨不同居群的开花物候特征。结果表明:胡杨、灰叶胡杨各居群均表现为雄株开花物候早于雌株,一般可授期开始较散粉期晚1～4d,结束较散粉期晚2～5d,并且居群散粉期和可授期的重叠期较长。在同一居群内,胡杨、灰叶胡杨同性单株间开花期的不一致性较高。两个种相比较,胡杨居群的开花进程比灰叶胡杨居群早2～5d,并且从每日开花株数累积分布来看,胡杨散粉期、可授期为双峰型,灰叶胡杨为单峰型。","1000-470X","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1041.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","zh","周正立;李志军;龚卫江;高山","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1041.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","zh","胡杨、灰叶胡杨开花生物学特性研究","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1041.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","zh","植物科学学报","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1041.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","zh","从居群水平研究了胡杨、灰叶胡杨不同居群的开花物候特征。结果表明:胡杨、灰叶胡杨各居群均表现为雄株开花物候早于雌株,一般可授期开始较散粉期晚1～4d,结束较散粉期晚2～5d,并且居群散粉期和可授期的重叠期较长。在同一居群内,胡杨、灰叶胡杨同性单株间开花期的不一致性较高。两个种相比较,胡杨居群的开花进程比灰叶胡杨居群早2～5d,并且从每日开花株数累积分布来看,胡杨散粉期、可授期为双峰型,灰叶胡杨为单峰型。","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1041.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","en","ZHOU Zheng-Li;LI Zhi-Jun;GONG Wei-Jiang;GAO Shan","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1041.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","en","Study on the Flowering Phenology in <I>Populus euphratica</I> and <I>Populus pruinosa</I>","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1041.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","en","Plant Science Journal","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1041.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","en","Flowering phenology characteristic of <I>Populus euphratica</I> and <I>Populus pruinosa</I> in different populations was studied.The results showed that:flowering phenology of male trees was earlier than that of female ones in all populations of <I>P.euphratica</I> and <I>P.pruinosa</I>.Generally,the beginning of female bud burst time was 1-4 days later and the end was 2-5 days later than those of male bud burst time,respectively.The overlap period of male and female bud burst time was longer.In the same population,the inconsistency of inflorescence were relatively high among same gender of <I>P.euphratica</I> or <I>P.pruinosa</I>.Compared <I>P.euphratica</I> with <I>P.pruinosa</I>,flowering time of <I>P.euphratica</I> population was 2-5 days earlier than that of <I>P.pruinosa</I>.According to cumulative distribution of flowering individuals each day,the male and female bud burst time of <I>P.euphratica</I> was bimodal type,and that of <I>P.pruinosa</I> was unimodal type.","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1041.shtml");
REPLACE INTO publications(authors,title,year,journal,spage,epage,volume,issue,pdf,url,date,abstract,issn,guid) values("陈倩;王跃进;王有为","宽叶缬草繁殖生物学特性研究","2005","植物科学学报",169,173,"23","2","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/article/downloadArticleFile.do?attachType=PDF&id=1144","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1144.shtml","2005-04-25","报道了药用植物宽叶缬草自然生长的历程,并对其不同生长环境及传粉环境下收获的瘦果千粒重和发芽率进行了统计分析。结果表明在不同的生长环境中,宽叶缬草瘦果千粒重有极显著差异;而在不同传粉环境中,养蜂实验区和防蜂实验区瘦果的发芽率有极显著差异,且前者高出后者近4倍。证明了通过增加传粉媒介蜜蜂的数量能够解决宽叶缬草人工栽培中的制种问题,从而使大面积栽培宽叶缬草成为可能,实现对宽叶缬草资源的可持续利用。","1000-470X","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1144.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","zh","陈倩;王跃进;王有为","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1144.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","zh","宽叶缬草繁殖生物学特性研究","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1144.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","zh","植物科学学报","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1144.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","zh","报道了药用植物宽叶缬草自然生长的历程,并对其不同生长环境及传粉环境下收获的瘦果千粒重和发芽率进行了统计分析。结果表明在不同的生长环境中,宽叶缬草瘦果千粒重有极显著差异;而在不同传粉环境中,养蜂实验区和防蜂实验区瘦果的发芽率有极显著差异,且前者高出后者近4倍。证明了通过增加传粉媒介蜜蜂的数量能够解决宽叶缬草人工栽培中的制种问题,从而使大面积栽培宽叶缬草成为可能,实现对宽叶缬草资源的可持续利用。","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1144.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","en","CHEN Qian;WANG Yue-Jin;WANG You-Wei","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1144.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","en","Study on the Reproductive Biological Characteristics of <I>Valeriana officinalis</I> L. var. <I>latifolia</I> Miq.","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1144.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","en","Plant Science Journal","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1144.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","en","This paper reports natural growth course of <I>Valeriana officinalis</I> L.var.<I>latifolia</I> Miq.,an important medicinal plant and the statistic analysis results of pollination experiment.There are prominent difference on the kilo grain weight of the achenia between wild and tame fields under the same pollination circumstance.While in the same background of planting and running,there are prominent difference on the burgeon rates of the achenia between beekeeping and no-bees plots,even the former is about 4 size higher than the latter.By artificially culturing and increasing the number of pollination medium,the problem that the low burgeon rates and the tinpot quality of the achenia will be settled.Thereby it is possible to culture this plant in large-scale and realize the sustainable usage of its resource.","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1144.shtml");
REPLACE INTO publications(authors,title,year,journal,spage,epage,volume,issue,pdf,url,date,abstract,issn,guid) values("吴娇;尤敏;王庆;王有为","冬凌草最佳采收期的研究","2005","植物科学学报",174,178,"23","2","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/article/downloadArticleFile.do?attachType=PDF&id=817","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract817.shtml","2005-04-25","以冬凌草的分枝数、单墩叶重及叶中冬凌草甲素的含量作为冬凌草药材产量和质量的评价指标,确定了河南淇县野生冬凌草和湖北广水、武汉野转家种冬凌草的最佳采收期,并分析了气象因素对冬凌草药材质量和产量的影响。结果表明:气象因素对引种地与原产地冬凌草的质量没有明显影响,药材叶中冬凌草甲素含量均在6月份左右达到峰值且十分接近;但气象因素对冬凌草产量则有影响,气候不同导致引种地野转家种药材的分枝数比原产地野生药材多2～4倍。综合质量和产量的考察结果,冬凌草的最佳采收期应定在其开花前,引种地武汉宜定在6月份,引种地广水宜定在6～7月份,原产地河南淇县宜定在6～8月份。","1000-470X","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract817.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","zh","吴娇;尤敏;王庆;王有为","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract817.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","zh","冬凌草最佳采收期的研究","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract817.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","zh","植物科学学报","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract817.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","zh","以冬凌草的分枝数、单墩叶重及叶中冬凌草甲素的含量作为冬凌草药材产量和质量的评价指标,确定了河南淇县野生冬凌草和湖北广水、武汉野转家种冬凌草的最佳采收期,并分析了气象因素对冬凌草药材质量和产量的影响。结果表明:气象因素对引种地与原产地冬凌草的质量没有明显影响,药材叶中冬凌草甲素含量均在6月份左右达到峰值且十分接近;但气象因素对冬凌草产量则有影响,气候不同导致引种地野转家种药材的分枝数比原产地野生药材多2～4倍。综合质量和产量的考察结果,冬凌草的最佳采收期应定在其开花前,引种地武汉宜定在6月份,引种地广水宜定在6～7月份,原产地河南淇县宜定在6～8月份。","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract817.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","en","WU Jiao;YOU Min;WANG Qing;WANG You-Wei","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract817.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","en","Study on the Optimum Harvest Time for <I>Isodon rubenscens</I>","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract817.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","en","Plant Science Journal","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract817.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","en","To find out the optimum harvest time for wild <I>Isodon rubenscens</I> in Qi County of Henan Province and introduced in Wuhan ,Guangshui of Hubei Province,we evaluated the yield and quality of <I>I.rubenscens</I> by the number of ramification,weight of leaves and content of rubescensine A of per-bundle plant.In addition,the effects of climate factors on yield and quality of <I>I.rubenscens</I> were analyzed.The results indicate that the effect of climate factors on the quality of <I>I.rubenscens</I> is not prominent,the content of rubescensine A in leaves of <I>I.rubenscens</I> in June reach approximate peak value in three areas.But climate factors have an effect on the yield of <I>I.rubenscens</I>,some of these factors can lead to the number of ramification on the plant in introduction areas is upwards to 2-4 times than the original area.To analysis all research results of the quality and yield of <I>I.rubenscens</I>,the optimum harvest time of <I>I.rubenscens</I> should be fixed ahead florescence.Therefore,the optimum harvest time of <I>I.rubenscens</I> is fixed from June to July in the introduced area-Guangshui of Hubei Province,and from June to August in the original area-Qi County of Henan Province.The studies can provide scientific basis for the Good Agriculture Practice of <I>I.rubenscens</I>.","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract817.shtml");
REPLACE INTO publications(authors,title,year,journal,spage,epage,volume,issue,pdf,url,date,abstract,issn,guid) values("蒲云海;刘贵华;李伟","竹叶眼子菜种子的萌发实验研究","2005","植物科学学报",179,182,"23","2","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/article/downloadArticleFile.do?attachType=PDF&id=1034","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1034.shtml","2005-04-25","竹叶眼子菜(<I>Potamogeton malaianus</I>)是长江中下游湖泊沉水植被中的优势种,在野外条件下主要依靠断枝繁殖,很少发现它的实生苗。在实验条件下对竹叶眼子菜进行了种子萌发研究,探讨了萌发基质、温度和光暗周期以及冷藏时间对种子萌发的影响。结果表明,干藏3个月后未处理种皮的种子发芽率极低,撕破种皮后显著地提高了种子发芽率。在水基质条件下,25℃最适宜竹叶眼子菜的萌发,光暗周期对种子发芽率有显著影响。冷藏6个月的种子发芽率最高,8个月时发芽率显著降低,表明竹叶眼子菜的种子不耐贮藏。还讨论了竹叶眼子菜种子休眠与萌发机制的生态学意义。","1000-470X","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1034.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","zh","蒲云海;刘贵华;李伟","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1034.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","zh","竹叶眼子菜种子的萌发实验研究","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1034.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","zh","植物科学学报","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1034.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","zh","竹叶眼子菜(<I>Potamogeton malaianus</I>)是长江中下游湖泊沉水植被中的优势种,在野外条件下主要依靠断枝繁殖,很少发现它的实生苗。在实验条件下对竹叶眼子菜进行了种子萌发研究,探讨了萌发基质、温度和光暗周期以及冷藏时间对种子萌发的影响。结果表明,干藏3个月后未处理种皮的种子发芽率极低,撕破种皮后显著地提高了种子发芽率。在水基质条件下,25℃最适宜竹叶眼子菜的萌发,光暗周期对种子发芽率有显著影响。冷藏6个月的种子发芽率最高,8个月时发芽率显著降低,表明竹叶眼子菜的种子不耐贮藏。还讨论了竹叶眼子菜种子休眠与萌发机制的生态学意义。","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1034.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","en","PU Yun-Hai;LIU Gui-Hua;LI Wei","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1034.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","en","Seed Germination of <I>Potamogeton malaianus</I>","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1034.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","en","Plant Science Journal","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1034.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","en","<I>Potamogeton malaianus</I> is a dominant submersed aquatic macrophyte that has colonized the lakes across the middle and lower reaches of the Changjiang River.Vegetative reproduction is prevalent in <I>P.malaianus</I> and is highly visible,because of the extraordinary capacity of this plant to spread by fragmentation.Because of this,sexual reproduction has been considered of limited importance and little is known about the seed germination of this species.Laboratory studies were conducted on seeds of <I>P.malaianus</I> to determine the substrate,temperature and light requirements necessary for maximum seed germination.Seed germination was also examined in different duration of cold storage.The results showed that few 3-month-old whole seeds germinated in all treatments,but rose after the seed coats were cracked.Optimum germination occurred in a temperature of 25℃ and water substrate.Photoperiod significantly effected the seed germination.Seed retain viability for a short period in the cold storage condition,the highest germination occurred in 6-month storage seeds.The ecological implications of such behavior are discussed.","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1034.shtml");
REPLACE INTO publications(authors,title,year,journal,spage,epage,volume,issue,pdf,url,date,abstract,issn,guid) values("黄秀丽;庄东红;胡忠;曲莹","南瓜属4个栽培种种子蛋白质电泳分析","2005","植物科学学报",183,187,"23","2","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/article/downloadArticleFile.do?attachType=PDF&id=1023","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1023.shtml","2005-04-25","通过聚丙烯酰胺凝胶电泳(PAGE)对南瓜属4个栽培种中国南瓜、印度南瓜、美洲南瓜及黑籽南瓜的12个品种种子蛋白组分进行了分析。结果显示,黑籽南瓜种子以盐溶蛋白条带居多;其它3个栽培种以水溶蛋白条带居多,其次为盐溶蛋白;4个栽培种酸溶蛋白条带均较少;醇溶蛋白未分离得到蛋白谱带。水溶、盐溶、酸溶蛋白电泳图谱显示各栽培种间蛋白谱带差异明显,同一栽培种品种间蛋白谱带较为一致。","1000-470X","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1023.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","zh","黄秀丽;庄东红;胡忠;曲莹","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1023.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","zh","南瓜属4个栽培种种子蛋白质电泳分析","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1023.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","zh","植物科学学报","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1023.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","zh","通过聚丙烯酰胺凝胶电泳(PAGE)对南瓜属4个栽培种中国南瓜、印度南瓜、美洲南瓜及黑籽南瓜的12个品种种子蛋白组分进行了分析。结果显示,黑籽南瓜种子以盐溶蛋白条带居多;其它3个栽培种以水溶蛋白条带居多,其次为盐溶蛋白;4个栽培种酸溶蛋白条带均较少;醇溶蛋白未分离得到蛋白谱带。水溶、盐溶、酸溶蛋白电泳图谱显示各栽培种间蛋白谱带差异明显,同一栽培种品种间蛋白谱带较为一致。","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1023.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","en","HUANG Xiu-Li;ZHUANG Dong-Hong;HU Zhong;QU Ying","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1023.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","en","Analysis of Electrophoretic Pattern of Seed Protein of Four Cultivated Species in <I>Cucurbita</I>","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1023.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","en","Plant Science Journal","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1023.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","en","Using polyacrylamide gel electrophoresis(PAGE)to anlysis seed protein ingredients of 12 cultivars from four cultivated species in genus <I>Cucurbita</I>:<I>C.moschato</I> Duch,<I>C.maxima</I> Duch,<I>C.pepo</I> L.,<I>C.ficifolia</I>.The results showed:Among seed proteins extracted with water,0.5 mol·L<SUP>-1</SUP> NaCl,0.1 mol·L<SUP>-1</SUP> Lacetic acid and 70% Ethanol,most of them are salt-soluble proteins in <I>C.ficifolia</I>;In the other three cultivated species,most of them are water-soluble proteins,with little salt-soluble proteins;All of the four species have very little acid-soluble proteins;In the examination,no alcohol-soluble protein bandings were obtained.The maps of water-soluble proteins,salt-soluble proteins,acid-soluble proteins showed great difference among the four species,but there were almost no difference among the cultivars of the same specie.","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1023.shtml");
REPLACE INTO publications(authors,title,year,journal,spage,epage,volume,issue,pdf,url,date,abstract,issn,guid) values("张改娜;何涛;王学仁;贾敬芬","盐胁迫下植物基因的表达与基因工程研究进展","2005","植物科学学报",188,195,"23","2","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/article/downloadArticleFile.do?attachType=PDF&id=1145","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1145.shtml","2005-04-25","在各种环境胁迫中,盐胁迫是造成作物减产的严重环境因素之一。随着植物分子生物学快速发展,植物耐盐性研究已深入到耐盐相关基因的克隆、基因的结构分析以及基因表达领域。文中就与植物耐盐性密切相关的小分子渗透物质、晚期胚胎发生富集蛋白(LEA)、通道蛋白、盐胁迫相关基因、信号传导基因和转录因子研究作了综述。同时对植物耐盐性研究作了简单的展望。","1000-470X","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1145.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","zh","张改娜;何涛;王学仁;贾敬芬","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1145.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","zh","盐胁迫下植物基因的表达与基因工程研究进展","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1145.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","zh","植物科学学报","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1145.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","zh","在各种环境胁迫中,盐胁迫是造成作物减产的严重环境因素之一。随着植物分子生物学快速发展,植物耐盐性研究已深入到耐盐相关基因的克隆、基因的结构分析以及基因表达领域。文中就与植物耐盐性密切相关的小分子渗透物质、晚期胚胎发生富集蛋白(LEA)、通道蛋白、盐胁迫相关基因、信号传导基因和转录因子研究作了综述。同时对植物耐盐性研究作了简单的展望。","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1145.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","en","ZHANG Gai-Na;HE Tao;WANG Xue-Ren;JIA Jing-Fen","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1145.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","en","Progress of Gene Expression and Gene Engineeringof Salt-tolerance in Plant","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1145.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","en","Plant Science Journal","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1145.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","en","Among various abiotic stresses,the salt stress is one of the most severe environmental factors responsible for the reduction of crop yield.With the development of molecular biology,the research of salt stress made great progress in gene cloning,analysis of its structure and gene expression.This paper reviewed small molecular osmotic substances,Late embryogensis abundant proteins,channel proteins,salt stress-related genes,signal transduction genes,transcriptional factors.Meanwhile prospects for the research are provided.","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1145.shtml");
REPLACE INTO publications(authors,title,year,journal,spage,epage,volume,issue,pdf,url,date,abstract,issn,guid) values("陈树思","蜈蚣草导管分子的观察","2005","植物科学学报",196,198,"23","2","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/article/downloadArticleFile.do?attachType=PDF&id=1035","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1035.shtml","2005-04-25","对蜈蚣草(<I>Pteris vittata</I>)叶轴中导管分子进行了观察。结果表明,其导管分子十分细长,均具长、且十分倾斜的梯状穿孔板,穿孔没有纹孔膜的残余,与侧壁上的梯纹纹孔有着明显的差异。","1000-470X","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1035.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","zh","陈树思","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1035.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","zh","蜈蚣草导管分子的观察","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1035.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","zh","植物科学学报","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1035.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","zh","对蜈蚣草(<I>Pteris vittata</I>)叶轴中导管分子进行了观察。结果表明,其导管分子十分细长,均具长、且十分倾斜的梯状穿孔板,穿孔没有纹孔膜的残余,与侧壁上的梯纹纹孔有着明显的差异。","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1035.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","en","CHEN Shu-Si","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1035.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","en","Study of Vessel Elements in <I>Pteris vittata</I>","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1035.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","en","Plant Science Journal","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1035.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","en","The vessel elements in rachis of <I>Pteris vittata</I> are observed and studied in this paper.The result shows that all of the vessel elements are very long.The scalariform perforation plates which are very long and gradient are in the either of end wall of vessel elements,there are a lot of perforations without pit membrane in these plates.The scalariform perforation plate in the <I>P.vittata</I> differs greatly from the scalariform pitting in side wall in conformation and structure.It is discussed that the vessel elements and the scalariform perforation plate in <I>P.vittata</I>.","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1035.shtml");
REPLACE INTO publications(authors,title,year,journal,spage,epage,volume,issue,pdf,url,date,abstract,issn,guid) values("刘庭凯;邹学新;赵婷婷;黄海波;王俊刚;麻琳;","桂花叶片的分形特征","2005","植物科学学报",199,202,"23","2","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/article/downloadArticleFile.do?attachType=PDF&id=1043","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1043.shtml","2005-04-25","提供了一种叶片分形维数的测定方法,并用其测定了桂花(<I>Osmanthus fragrans</I> Lour)的叶片分形维数。通过分析发现:(1)桂花叶片具有典型的分形特征并且这种分形特征可以用分形理论的一般方法加以研究;(2)同一株桂花树的成熟叶片在统计意义上具有相同的分形维数;(3)对于桂花这个物种的成熟叶片在统计意义上具有相同的分形维数。由此推测同一种植物的成熟叶片(或者其他构件)具有相同分形维数。最后提出创建植物分形分类学的设想。","1000-470X","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1043.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","zh","刘庭凯;邹学新;赵婷婷;黄海波;王俊刚;麻琳;","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1043.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","zh","桂花叶片的分形特征","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1043.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","zh","植物科学学报","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1043.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","zh","提供了一种叶片分形维数的测定方法,并用其测定了桂花(<I>Osmanthus fragrans</I> Lour)的叶片分形维数。通过分析发现:(1)桂花叶片具有典型的分形特征并且这种分形特征可以用分形理论的一般方法加以研究;(2)同一株桂花树的成熟叶片在统计意义上具有相同的分形维数;(3)对于桂花这个物种的成熟叶片在统计意义上具有相同的分形维数。由此推测同一种植物的成熟叶片(或者其他构件)具有相同分形维数。最后提出创建植物分形分类学的设想。","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1043.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("authors","en","LIU Ting-Kai;ZOU Xue-Xin;ZHAO Ting-Ting;HUANG Hai-Bo;WANG Jun-Gang;MA Lin;","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1043.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("title","en","Fractal Characteristics of Leaves of <I>Osmanthus fragrans</I> Lour","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1043.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("journal","en","Plant Science Journal","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1043.shtml");
REPLACE INTO multilingual(`key`,language,value,guid) values("abstract","en","This paper offers a method to measure leaf’s fractal dimension(FD)by introducing the box-counting dimension, one method the fractal theory provided.The scanned photos of mature leaves are treated according to the box-counting dimension.We use this method to measure the leaf’s FD of <I>Osmanthus fragrans</I> Lour.By analyzing the result, we find that:(1)The goodness of linear fit of double-logarithmic plot of the number of boxes to box size is significantly great:all the absolute values of coefficient of correlation are grcatcr than 0.999 1 that is very close to 1,the expectation.So we conclude that leases have typical fractal characteristics,which can be studied by fractal theory.(2)The FDs of all leaves of Tree 0.1 from the sample are between 1.7258 and 1.8880,with an average of 1.8065,a standard deviation of 0.0393 and a coefficient of variation(CV)of 2.7180%,which imply the low discreteness.A,nd all the data are normally distrilauted as vsrell.Other trees in the sample share the same case,so we conclude that the mature leaves of the same tree have the same FD statistically.(3)The ANOVA using rite completely randnm model shows that the differences between the 10 sample trees are not significant:F=0.706<F(9,490,0.05)=1.899,WHICH <i of Leaves mature the that means>Osmanthus fragrans</I> Lour share the same FD statistically.Therefore we presume that the mature leaves(or other mndule)of the same species share the same FD statistically.Finally we prnpnse an idea a, founding plant fractal taxonnmy.","http://www.whzwxyj.cn/CN/abstract/abstract1043.shtml");
